<br>
Other than that, make sure that your buffing, etc, doesn't take so long that you get giant backspawn, and that everyone knows the way in (don't lose folks falling into the pits, this always sucks).  Oh, and tell your troops to put 'Walk' on before they charge into her, so that if they do get feared, they don't get themselves lost, fall in a pit, or worse, train the raiding party...<br>
<br>
Best of luck,<br>
Nydia Ywalmoriel<br>
